env PAGER=cat man timing_constraint_enable_detailed_report_invalid _begin_end_points
Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_constr...gin_end_points(25.10)    timing_constr...gin_end_points(25.10)

Name
       timing_constraint_enable_detailed_report_invalid_begin_end_points

Syntax
       timing_constraint_enable_detailed_report_invalid_begin_end_points

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables  detailed  reporting of invalid begin/end points specified with
       the set_false_path/set_multicycle_path constraints.

       When set to false, the software checks only the structural end points.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

